Summary
  Adds events that can be used for hot tracking.
Description
  TJvHeaderControl is a header control that supports extended features. You can use OnMouseEnter and
  OnMouseLeave to alter the controls look or behavior, when the user moves the mouse pointer over the
  control.
  
  Use property HintColor to change the color of the hint boxes for the header control.

